station cook
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number: 1
Definition:a cook for single staff on a station, located in a cookshop or cookhouse [and often assisted by an offsider .]
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
